#: mater --> matron
#: pater --> patron
#{{cattag|Physics}}: Suffix used to form nouns denoting elementary [[particles]] {{italbrac|proton}}, quanta {{italbrac|photon}}, [[molecular]] units {{italbrac|codon}}, or [[substance]]s {{italbrac|interferon}}.
#{{cattag|Genetics}}: Suffix used to form names of [[genetic]] units, such as [[codon]] or [[recon]].

